  "detailed_description": "<strong>\"Unravel the mystery of a fallen tear on its journey back to the surface!\"</strong><br><br><i>Tears Fall Low</i> is a mesmerizing 2D platformer filled with inventive mechanics and challenging gameplay. Explore a rich and diverse world, as you climb out of dark caverns towards the surface!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/5fa76c1c0882da6a59c8d134c7ab169c.poster.avif?t=1685833591\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/5fa76c1c0882da6a59c8d134c7ab169c.webm?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/5fa76c1c0882da6a59c8d134c7ab169c.mp4?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As a fallen tear, embark on a journey through the hidden depths of the Earth, overcoming terrible perils. Each area holds its own secrets and dangers, presenting unique obstacles and challenges that test your skills and wit.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/4bb0ca71538114819eaea61dc14f8f54.poster.avif?t=1685833591\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/4bb0ca71538114819eaea61dc14f8f54.webm?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/4bb0ca71538114819eaea61dc14f8f54.mp4?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unlock your true potential as you progress through the game, and face the formidable monsters beneath the surface. Delve deep into a simple but captivating story that unfolds in unexpected and strange ways...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/98289f7d4f6ed0ba2ae60650e9493016.poster.avif?t=1685833591\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/98289f7d4f6ed0ba2ae60650e9493016.webm?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/98289f7d4f6ed0ba2ae60650e9493016.mp4?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mysterious and Engaging World<br></li><li>Challenging Platforming<br></li><li>Intriguing Story with Captivating Themes</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>\"Unravel the mystery of a fallen tear on its journey back to the surface!\"</strong><br><br><i>Tears Fall Low</i> is a mesmerizing 2D platformer filled with inventive mechanics and challenging gameplay. Explore a rich and diverse world, as you climb out of dark caverns towards the surface!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/5fa76c1c0882da6a59c8d134c7ab169c.poster.avif?t=1685833591\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/5fa76c1c0882da6a59c8d134c7ab169c.webm?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/5fa76c1c0882da6a59c8d134c7ab169c.mp4?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As a fallen tear, embark on a journey through the hidden depths of the Earth, overcoming terrible perils. Each area holds its own secrets and dangers, presenting unique obstacles and challenges that test your skills and wit.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/4bb0ca71538114819eaea61dc14f8f54.poster.avif?t=1685833591\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/4bb0ca71538114819eaea61dc14f8f54.webm?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/4bb0ca71538114819eaea61dc14f8f54.mp4?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unlock your true potential as you progress through the game, and face the formidable monsters beneath the surface. Delve deep into a simple but captivating story that unfolds in unexpected and strange ways...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/98289f7d4f6ed0ba2ae60650e9493016.poster.avif?t=1685833591\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/98289f7d4f6ed0ba2ae60650e9493016.webm?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/98289f7d4f6ed0ba2ae60650e9493016.mp4?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mysterious and Engaging World<br></li><li>Challenging Platforming<br></li><li>Intriguing Story with Captivating Themes</li></ul>",
